attr.title: COMEBACK
attr.desc: In a cold and empty world, only you and your peculiar light weapon can help you survive. Use it to trap enemies, kill them and return home.
attr.inst: download the zip from https://guselect.itch.io/comeback and put the game files in ports/comeback/assets
attr.inst_md: download the zip from [itch.io](https://guselect.itch.io/comeback) and put the game files in ports/comeback/assets.
